Odd rumors about #coronavirus according to WHO's "myth busting" post: 
- Can eating garlic help prevent infection with the new coronavirus? Answer: No
- Does putting on sesame oil block the new coronavirus from entering the body? Answer: No https://t.co/AICouAVKzB
